{"tid":995121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【阿婆都呃】騙子疑用泰銖扮港紙　八旬砵仔糕婆婆再遭殃","createTime":"2019-01-25T08:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T08:09:08.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6f7a442709648a0b81d7efa07be1bfb565289b55","tid":995121,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:00:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>騙子疑用泰銖扮港紙　八旬砵仔糕婆婆再遭殃</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/bkn-20190125135831726-0125_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fbkn-20190125135831726-0125_00822_001.html&d=9I4BeS4eQ9jGYJ6jP2Db68PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=9e9165e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/bkn-20190125135831726-0125_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/photo/bkn-20190125135831726-0125_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190125154547\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190125135831726-0125_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190125154547&h=a53cadc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連阿婆都呃！<br />\n<br />\n挨年近晚，又到了騙子出沒的高峰期。有網民在Facebook群組「西環變幻時」發貼，指近日有人以泰銖魚目混珠，欺騙八旬砵仔糕婆婆，呼籲街坊小心被騙。<br />\n<br />\n據發貼者稱，他從婆婆口中得悉，一名年約30歲的男子在周四（24日）以100泰銖向婆婆購買兩個砵仔糕，「仲大聲講，找數90」。按現時匯率換算，100泰銖相等約25港元，砵仔糕現時售價為5元一個，即她被騙去約75港元。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民怒斥騙徒無恥︰「老人家都蝦，正X街」、「連阿婆都呃」、「婆婆找90港幣，變了請咗嗰位人兄吃」。有人善意提醒︰「我哋幫襯婆婆時，大家幫吓眼！」<br />\n<br />\n婆婆在餐廳門口擺檔30多年，售賣砵仔糕及糯米糍，於附近一帶享負盛名。三年前，她開檔期間慘被小偷盜去手袋，引起廣大市民的關注，幸沒有太大損失。"},{"pid":"179562a4deb6078236d1266da3398f7c25a8ead1","tid":995121,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/photo/bkn-20190125135831726-0125_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190125154547\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190125135831726-0125_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190125154547&h=fd2204e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人疑以100泰銖充當港幣買砵仔糕，更要求找90蚊。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/photo/bkn-20190125135831726-0125_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190125154547\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190125135831726-0125_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190125154547&h=7c0761cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n婆婆於西環擺檔賣砵仔糕及糯米糍。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/photo/bkn-20190125135831726-0125_00822_001_04p.jpg?20190125154547\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190125135831726-0125_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20190125154547&h=4d1f56b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三年前，婆婆曾被人偷去手袋。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"8f261d8ba3a8183057573757dd1be9c7303a75fb","tid":995121,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:02:04.000Z","msg":"屌....不得好死"},{"pid":"41a614218a5c81cf4e932521bff3e947fa137b48","tid":995121,"uid":189528,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:03:11.000Z","msg":"到底有幾失敗既人先會去呃阿婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d0aa0040fc554a4636011b6d9649d8f92a1c33","tid":995121,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:04:05.000Z","msg":"食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ccd1d1520e1ab4f41087ce023ac845326c53cbc","tid":995121,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:05:06.000Z","msg":"有冇西環巴打知邊個位？想去幫襯下買砵仔榚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cad23a8a364b0694670b3ab4b9cf5fc6cb1ffe","tid":995121,"uid":52130,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7ccd1d1520e1ab4f41087ce023ac845326c53cbc","tid":995121,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:05:06.000Z","msg":"有冇西環巴打知邊個位？想去幫襯下買砵仔榚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:08:27.000Z","msg":"西環德記門口"},{"pid":"591f4e76d2fcffffa21f0dc092890b843f776645","tid":995121,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"85cad23a8a364b0694670b3ab4b9cf5fc6cb1ffe","tid":995121,"uid":52130,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7ccd1d1520e1ab4f41087ce023ac845326c53cbc","tid":995121,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:05:06.000Z","msg":"有冇西環巴打知邊個位？想去幫襯下買砵仔榚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:08:27.000Z","msg":"西環德記門口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:09:08.000Z","msg":"Thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}